WEBVTT

00:01:29.198 --> 00:01:31.932
Thanks to Bonobos
for sponsoring this episode.

00:01:31.956 --> 00:01:37.544
(Music)

00:01:37.568 --> 00:01:40.977
Even if you have a boss,
you still have to manage yourself.

00:01:43.212 --> 00:01:46.399
You make choices every day
about which tasks to prioritize,

00:01:46.423 --> 00:01:47.911
who to invite to a meeting,

00:01:47.935 --> 00:01:50.561
how to start digging out
of your overflowing inbox.

00:01:51.229 --> 00:01:52.866
But if you're like most people,

00:01:52.890 --> 00:01:54.923
you've craved even more freedom.

00:01:55.328 --> 00:01:57.687
It's a theme that runs across
centuries of work.

00:01:58.333 --> 00:01:59.484
In medieval times,

00:01:59.508 --> 00:02:01.461
mercenaries became freelancers